trafficserver

This is the trafficserver module. \o/

manage installation and configuration of trafficserver.

Currently supported modes: Forward, Reverse and mixed. Supported Platforms: Debuntu.

WARNING: This module will not work under Ruby 1.8 as expected.
It makes heavy use of hashes as datastructures. Traffic Server expects certain
configs to be in a given order. That's a promise that Ruby 1.8 Hashes don't
deliever. So upgrade *now* to 1.9 or 2.0. Go ahead.

